#: ../../../integrations/editors.md:360
msgid ""
"[conform.nvim](https://github.com/stevearc/conform.nvim) is a lightweight "
"formatter plugin for Neovim. It supports _Black_ out of the box as long as "
"`black` is available in your `PATH`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../integrations/editors.md:364
msgid "Install `black` (e.g. `pip install black` or `pipx install black`)"
